Over time, we may develop habits that are harmful to our health, hinder our performance at work, offset our efforts for a better life or destroy our relationships. With some willpower, strength, courage and support, we can kick these bad habits and start the year with a clean slate.You have to love yourself enough to want to be a better person. You have to want your loved ones to know and experience a better version of you. You have to love yourself enough to want to move out of your old circumstances and want a new experience.&nbsp;